aweme_list.desc: ✨Pasta Pomodoro✨ is a very classic dish known for its simplicity. Various versions of this recipe, but the key is very good ingredients. The result is a beautiful blend of tomato’s which are complemented by aromatic garlic and fragrant basil. I of course use fresh pasta here. It’s quick and comforting, topped with lots of grated Parmesan cheese. A perfect representation of a fave italian recipe with its elegance in simplicity. Enjoy! 🍅 🍝✨💖 #pasta #pastarecipe #homecooking #cooking #dinnerideas #pastatiktok #pastalover #pastagirl #homemade #pastacooking

✨Pasta Pomodoro✨ is a very classic dish known for its simplicity. Various versions of this recipe, but the key is very good ingredients. The result is a beautiful blend of tomato’s which are complemented by aromatic garlic and fragrant basil. I of course use fresh pasta here. It’s quick and comforting, topped with lots of grated Parmesan cheese. A perfect representation of a fave italian recipe with its elegance in simplicity. Enjoy! 🍅 🍝✨💖

#pasta #pastarecipe #homecooking #cooking #dinnerideas #pastatiktok #pastalover #pastagirl #homemade #pastacooking
